\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 20 
\f1\b0 Then the mother of Zebedee\'92s sons came to Jesus with her sons and, kneeling down, asked a favor of him.\cf2 \strokec2 \

\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 21 
\f1\b0 \'93What is it you want?\'94 he asked.\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 She said, \'93Grant that one of these two sons of mine may sit at your right and the other at your left in your kingdom.\'94\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 22 
\f1\b0 \'93You don\'92t know what you are asking,\'94 Jesus said to them. \'93Can you drink the cup I am going to drink?\'94\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 \'93We can,\'94 they answered.\cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0

\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 23 
\f1\b0 Jesus said to them, \'93You will indeed drink from my cup, but to sit at my right or left is not for me to grant. These places belong to those for whom they have been prepared by my Father.\'94\cf2 \strokec2 \

\f0\b \cf5 \strokec5 24 
\f1\b0 When the ten heard about this, they were indignant with the two brothers. 
\f0\b 25 
\f1\b0 Jesus called them together and said, \'93You know that the rulers of the Gentiles lord it over them, and their high officials exercise authority over them. 
\f0\b 26 
\f1\b0 Not so with you. Instead, whoever wants to become great among you must be your servant, 
\f0\b 27 
\f1\b0 and whoever wants to be first must be your slave\'97 
\f0\b 28 
\f1\b0 just as the Son of Man did not come to be served, but to serve, and to give his life as a ransom for many.\'94 \'a0Matthew 20\cf2 \strokec2 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Leadership is NOT about LORDING power OVER others but about LEVERAGING power FOR others.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf5 \strokec5 Not so with you. \cf2 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf2 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Those are powerful words\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Here we see Jesus trying to shift the disciples view of leadership and what it means to be a leader\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Because of who Jesus is and what He did on the cross\'85He has the power and influence to change our perspective on how to lead.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl1\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Now most people would agree with this on the surface...\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 I don\'92t know of many who are walking around and thinking to themselves\'85I can\'92t wait to LORD it over others how powerful I am over them.\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 But\'85how do you see your power/influence\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl2\cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 As a boss\'85are they there for you or the other way around?\uc0\u8232 \
\ls4\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
